{"tid":177460,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【尋晚又一個】男子上水站墮軌捲車底亡","createTime":"2017-03-29T01:16:57.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-29T01:50:24.000Z","uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8dfe3d6f73a218c167f5fcb92b45010187a8d4f8","tid":177460,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T01:16:57.000Z","msg":"五日內第二宗 男子上水站墮軌捲車底亡<br />\n<br />\n東鐵上水站南行線發生墮軌事件，凌晨零一分，一名55歲男子從月台跳落路軌，駛至一輛列車煞掣不及，將男子捲入車底，消防員到場將墮軌男子救出，惟救護員證實已經死亡，路軌留下一灘血迹。據知男子因家事問題不開心，警方沒有撿獲遺書，調查後相信無可疑。東鐵列車服務受阻約55鐘。<br />\n<br />\n上星期五早上，一名患有高血壓、並曾經中風的65歲姓李男子疑因病厭世，在上水站往羅湖月台墮軌，被駛過列車輾開三截，當場死亡。<br />\n相關新聞：<br />\n男子上水站跳軌被輾斃<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2nxj4sh\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2nxj4sh&d=u6uLjzzFZj4TH%2F5rj7Ekc7%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=d23ddfa4\" target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2nxj4sh</a><br />\n<br />\n24小時求助熱線︰<br />\n香港撒瑪利亞防止自殺會熱線︰23892222<br />\n撒瑪利亞會熱線(多種語言)︰28960000<br />\n生命熱線︰23820000<br />\n東華三院芷若園熱線︰18281<br />\n社會福利署熱線︰23432255<br />\n醫院管理局精神健康專線(24小時精神健康熱線諮詢服務)：24667350<br />\n明愛向晴熱線：18288<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/breaking/20170329/56493945\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fbreaking%2F20170329%2F56493945&d=u6uLjzzFZj4TH%2F5rj7Ekc7%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=dcb53be5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fbreaking%2F20170329%2F56493945&h=ddf2b40f\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/breaking/20170329/56493945</a>"},{"pid":"b98235bab4f541383c24c3399b8d314355f32f16","tid":177460,"uid":30835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T01:19:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"641bf54a90e7e8511a9f198b11d7b852209b1d6b","tid":177460,"uid":90791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T01:21:11.000Z","msg":"安樂死 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7541e367f8499b3a0af4cba9f70f6ba30c46823d","tid":177460,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T01:23:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>安樂死 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n點都好過夾在月台邊打轉。<br />\n<br />\n不過東鐵果啲闊過海底隧道，無事既。"},{"pid":"becb4afee1ddbb54a09308c157098a7e84e32363","tid":177460,"uid":10692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T01:50:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}